text: Yohandris Andújar de la Cruz (born 5 July 1990) is a Dominican sprinter. He competed in the men's 4 × 100 metres relay at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Dominican Republic male sprinters Category:Olympic athletes of the Dominican Republic Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
